chunk-92ae10ec56afd21a8da50f6e9109d55a.description: ERASER is an organization responsible for tokenizing datasets using the spaCy library and releasing train/validation/test splits. It also involves tokenizing datasets into sentences, with the exception of e-SNLI and CoS-E.
Upwork is a platform used to hire annotators for the Movies and Evidence Inference datasets.
Amazon Mechanical Turk is a platform used to collect reference comprehensive rationales for the BoolQ dataset.
